Archipelago is a Multiworld Randomiser software that lets multiple games be randomized with each of their items shuffled between all the given "worlds".

It has support for a large amount of games, some that migh surprise new players.

These include:
- Common Metroidvanias:
  - Legend of Zelda
  - Super Metroid
  - Hollow Knight
- Roguelikes:
  - Risk of Rain 2
  - Slay the Spire
- And the suprising bunch:
  - Stardew Valley (farming sim)
  - Wargroove (Advance Wars-inspired tactics game)
  - Minecraft
  - Terraria
  - VVVVVV (gimmick platformer)
  - Super Mario World
  - Super Mario 64
  - Muse Dash
